OL,3,CPETA call for ban on Sark's Sheep
OL,4,CRacing Festival
OL,6,FAn international animal rights group
OL,7,Fhas called on Sark to end its
OL,8,Ftraditional Sheep Racing Festival.
OL,10,FThe Sark Sheep Racing Festival is an
OL,11,Fannual event where sheep race down a
OL,12,Fgrass track with teddy bear jockeys
OL,13,Fstrapped to their backs.
OL,15,FThe event takes place in the summer,
OL,16,Fwith proceeds going to the Professor
OL,17,FCharles Saint Sark Medical Trust.
