OL,3,CPETA call for ban on Sark's Sheep
OL,4,CRacing Festival
OL,6,FHowever, the People for the Ethical
OL,7,FTreatment of Animals (PETA) has
OL,8,Fwritten a letter to the Sark Carnival
OL,9,FCommittee to urge them to race
OL,10,F"willing human participants" instead.
OL,12,FThe Committee met to discuss the
OL,13,Fletter, and say they will consult with
OL,14,Fthe States of Guernsey vet before
OL,15,Fmaking a decision on the best course
OL,16,Fof action to take.
OL,18,FThe letter reads: "Sheep are many
OL,19,Fthings, but they are not clowns for
OL,20,Fhuman entertainment or professional
OL,21,Fathletes on whom to wager.
