OL,3,CPETA call for ban on Sark's Sheep
OL,4,CRacing Festival
OL,6,F"They are gentle, good-natured,
OL,7,Fplayful, and loving animals with
OL,8,Fcomplex emotions, (and) are also
OL,9,Fprotective parents and resourceful
OL,10,Fproblem-solvers. Above all, they're
OL,11,Findividuals who feel pain and fear.
OL,13,F"Holding sheep races sends a dangerous
OL,14,Fmessage to young people that it is
OL,15,Facceptable to objectify animals and
OL,16,Fuse them as little more than living
OL,17,Fprops.
