OL,3,CPETA call for ban on Sark's Sheep
OL,4,CRacing Festival
OL,6,F"The sheep do not consent to
OL,7,Fparticipating in this confusing and
OL,8,Fstressful event and should be left in
OL,9,Fpeace."
OL,11,FPETA is an animal rights group against
OL,12,Fthe use of animals in laboratories,
OL,13,Fthe food industry, the clothing trade,
OL,14,Fand the entertainment business.
OL,16,FThey have historically called for bans
OL,17,Fand changes in the UK to protect
OL,18,Fanimals, from phasing out police dogs
OL,19,Fto changing the name of The Sly Old
OL,20,FFox pub in Birmingham, calling it
OL,21,F"derogatory".
