OL,3,CPETA call for ban on Sark's Sheep
OL,4,CRacing Festival
OL,6,FDawn Carr, PETA Vice President of
OL,7,FVegan Corporate Projects, says: "Sheep
OL,8,Fdo not consent to participating in
OL,9,Fthis confusing and stressful event and
OL,10,Fshould be left in peace.
OL,12,F"There are plenty of fun and family-
OL,13,Ffriendly rural activities without
OL,14,Fanimals that can be celebrated.
OL,16,F"How about a 'potato' and spoon race,
OL,17,Fa hobby horse jump competition, or a
OL,18,Ftractor tug of war?"
